headline: Airbnb (NasdaqGS:ABNB) Reports $154 Million Net Income Decline in Q1 2025 Earnings
summary: Airbnb (NasdaqGS:ABNB) recently announced its Q1 2025 earnings, demonstrating a sales increase to $2,272 million, though net income declined to $154 million from the previous year. Alongside this, the company provided optimistic guidance for Q2 2025, expecting revenue growth of up to 11%, aided by Easter holiday timing.
